Nollywood actress Regina Daniels has taken to social media to alert her fans about a big announcement she will be making with her husband. The young actress, who married elderly businessman and politician Ned Nwoko, made this known via her IG stories. She said; “Hello fam! My husband and I have an announcement. Wait for it!” Some fans have been going ahead of her to assume that she might be pregnant for Mr. Nwoko. Regina has been in the news for the better part of the year after reports first surfaced that she had tied the knot with a much older man. He has since been splashing money on Regina and her family since their romance started. Source